com.ibm.team.build.common.builddefinition

Interface IBuildDefinitionTemplate


  • public interface IBuildDefinitionTemplate
    A combination of build configuration elements, used to initialize a build definition.

      • getConfigurationElementIds

        java.lang.String[] getConfigurationElementIds()
        Get the default configuration element ids that are part of this template. The elements are in the array in the order declared in the template extension.
        Returns:
        An array of element ids. Never empty or null.

      • getAvailableConfigurationElementIds

        java.lang.String[] getAvailableConfigurationElementIds()
        Get the configuration element ids that are available, but are not selected by default for this template. The elements are in the array in the order declared in the template extension.
        Returns:
        An array of element ids. May be empty, but never null.

      • getConfigurationPropertyTemplateValue

        java.lang.String getConfigurationPropertyTemplateValue(java.lang.String configurationElementId,
                                                       java.lang.String propertyName)
        Get the default value specified for a configuration property in a certain configuration element for this template.
        Parameters:
        configurationElementId - The id of the configuration element
        propertyName - The name of the configuration property
        Returns:
        The default value configured in this template for the configuration property in the configuration element. Can return null if no such element id is configured, it has not a property with that name, or this has no default value specified
